## 6. UI/UX Requirements

### 6.1 Visual Design

**Archetype Grid**:
- **Card size**: 200px Ã— 240px on desktop
- **Spacing**: 24px gap between cards
- **Color coding**: Each archetype has subtle color accent (see iconography)
- **Typography**:
  - Archetype name: 20px semibold
  - Tagline: 14px regular
  - Icon: 56px emoji
- **Hover state**: Card lifts 4px, shadow increases, "Learn More" button appears
- **Selected state**: Purple border (3px), checkmark badge in top-right

**Detail Modal**:
- **Width**: 800px max on desktop, full screen on mobile
- **Scroll**: Content scrolls within modal, backdrop stays fixed
- **Sections**: Clear visual hierarchy with dividers
- **CTA Buttons**: Large, prominent at bottom
- **Close**: X button top-right, ESC key, click outside

**Combination Interface**:
- **Radio buttons**: Large, clear selection
- **Visual preview**: Show both archetype icons side-by-side
- **Combined name**: Displays prominently when combination selected

### 6.2 Component Structure
```
ArchetypeBuilder/
â”œâ”€â”€ ArchetypeBuilderScreen.jsx       // Main orchestrator
â”œâ”€â”€ SelectionMethodChoice.jsx        // AI/Grid/Deep choice
â”œâ”€â”€ AIArchetypeSuggestion.jsx       // AI recommendation path
â”œâ”€â”€ ArchetypeGrid.jsx                // 12-card grid
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ ArchetypeCard.jsx           // Individual archetype card
â”œâ”€â”€ ArchetypeDetailModal.jsx        // Full archetype details
â”œâ”€â”€ DeepBuilderQuestionnaire.jsx    // Question-based selection
â”œâ”€â”€ CombinationSelector.jsx         // Secondary archetype selection
â”œâ”€â”€ DarkSidesExplorer.jsx           // Too much/too little
â”œâ”€â”€ JourneyMapper.jsx               // Character transformation arc
â”‚   â””â”€â”€ JourneyVisualizer.jsx       // Visual journey diagram
â””â”€â”€ ArchetypePreview.jsx            // Summary/confirmation view
```

### 6.3 Responsive Behavior
- **Desktop (â‰¥1024px)**: 4-column grid, side-by-side detail views
- **Tablet (768-1023px)**: 3-column grid, modal details
- **Mobile (<768px)**: 2-column grid (or 1 column for small phones), full-screen modals

### 6.4 Accessibility
- **Keyboard navigation**: 
  - Tab through archetype cards
  - Enter to select/open details
  - Arrow keys to navigate grid
  - ESC to close modals
- **Screen reader**: 
  - Announce archetype selections
  - Read full descriptions on focus
  - Announce combination results
- **ARIA labels**: All interactive elements properly labeled
- **Focus management**: Focus moves logically through flow
- **Color contrast**: Text meets WCAG AA (4.5:1) on all backgrounds

### 6.5 Loading & Empty States

**AI Suggestion Loading**:
```
Analyzing your story...
