8. Success Metrics
8.1 Primary Metrics

Usage rate: 70%+ of users engage with archetype builder
Completion rate: 85%+ select an archetype (vs. skipping)
AI suggestion acceptance: 50%+ accept AI suggestion when offered
Deep builder completion: 60%+ complete full questionnaire when started
Combination usage (Comprehensive Mode): 40%+ add secondary archetype
Journey mapping usage (Comprehensive Mode): 30%+ map character transformation

8.2 Secondary Metrics

Selection method distribution:

Grid browsing: 50%
AI suggested: 30%
Deep builder: 20%


Detail view engagement: 70%+ view full archetype details before selecting
Dark sides exploration (Comprehensive): 35%+ configure dark sides
Time spent: Average 2-4 minutes (Quick), 8-12 minutes (Comprehensive)
Archetype distribution: Track which archetypes are most/least selected

8.3 Quality Metrics

Archetype-story alignment: Do selected archetypes make sense for story types?
Combination coherence: Are combined archetypes logical pairings?
User satisfaction: Post-selection survey "Does this archetype fit your character?" >4/5
Retention in final story: 90%+ keep selected archetype through completion

