- Show 'Too Much' and 'Too Little' dark sides
- Checkboxes to enable/disable each
- Descriptions of what each dark side means
- Save to character state

JOURNEY MAPPING:
- Select start archetype (dropdown: balanced/too much/too little/different)
- Text area for transformation catalyst
- Select end archetype state
- Visual journey diagram (start â†’ transformation â†’ end)
- Save complete journey to state

Use visual elements: timeline, arrows, archetype icons.
```

**Session 5: Deep Builder Questionnaire** (90 min)
```
Prompt to Claude:
"Build Deep Builder Questionnaire for archetype selection.

Requirements:
- Display questions one at a time
- 8-10 questions with 4-6 options each
- Progress indicator
- Calculate archetype scores based on answers
- Show final recommendation with confidence
- Display top 3 alternatives
- User can accept or explore further

Questions: [provide deepBuilderQuestions array]
Scoring logic: [provide calculateArchetypeScores function]
```

