12.3 State Management Pattern
javascript// In StoryContext
const [storyData, setStoryData] = useState({
  // ... other story data
  character: {
    primary: null,
    secondary: null,
    combined: null,
    journey: null,
    selectionMethod: null,
    selectedAt: null,
    isSimplified: false
  }
});

// Helper functions
const selectPrimaryArchetype = (archetypeId) => {
  const archetype = archetypesLibrary[archetypeId];
  setStoryData(prev => ({
    ...prev,
    character: {
      ...prev.character,
      primary: {
        id: archetype.id,
        name: archetype.name,
        icon: archetype.icon,
        tagline: archetype.tagline,
        values: archetype.values,
        gift: archetype.gift,
        darkSides: {
          tooMuch: { ...archetype.darkSides.tooMuch, enabled: false },
          tooLittle: { ...archetype.darkSides.tooLittle, enabled: false }
        }
      },
      selectedAt: new Date().toISOString()
    }
  }));
};

const addSecondaryArchetype = (archetypeId) => {
  const primary = storyData.character.primary.id;
  const combination = archetypeCombinations[primary][archetypeId];
  
  setStoryData(prev => ({
    ...prev,
    character: {
      ...prev.character,
      secondary: {
        id: archetypeId,
        name: archetypesLibrary[archetypeId].name,
        icon: archetypesLibrary[archetypeId].icon
      },
      combined: {
        name: combination.name,
        description: combination.description,
        primaryInfluence: 60,
        secondaryInfluence: 40
      }
    }
  }));
};

const configureDarkSides = (tooMuch, tooLittle) => {
  setStoryData(prev => ({
    ...prev,
    character: {
      ...prev.character,
      primary: {
        ...prev.character.primary,
        darkSides: {
          tooMuch: { ...prev.character.primary.darkSides.tooMuch, enabled: tooMuch },
          tooLittle: { ...prev.character.primary.darkSides.tooLittle, enabled: tooLittle }
        }
      }
    }
  }));
};

const saveCharacterJourney = (journeyData) => {
  setStoryData(prev => ({
    ...prev,
    character: {
      ...prev.character,
      journey: journeyData
    }
  }));
};
12.4 Testing Checklist

 All 12 archetypes display correctly in grid
 Archetype detail modal shows complete information
 AI suggestion calls API and displays recommendation
 Grid selection works (click, select, save)
 Secondary archetype combinations work
 Combined archetype names display correctly
 Dark sides configuration saves properly
 Journey mapper creates visual diagram
 Deep builder questionnaire calculates scores accurately
 Quick Mode simplification works (no combinations/journey)
 Comprehensive Mode shows all features
 State persists across page refreshes
 Saves to Supabase correctly
 Responsive on mobile/tablet/desktop
 Keyboard navigation works
 Screen reader accessibility
 All animations smooth and performant


13. Next Steps
13.1 Immediate Actions

Validate archetypes library: Review all 12 archetypes with stakeholders
Test combinations matrix: Ensure all 66+ combinations are documented
Design review: Finalize UI mockups for grid and detail modal
AI prompt testing: Generate sample suggestions for different story types

13.2 Post-MVP Enhancements

Video introductions: Short video explaining each archetype
Archetype quiz: Fun personality quiz to find your archetype
Multi-character support: Define hero, antagonist, mentor archetypes
Archetype library: Save favorite combinations for future stories
Cultural variations: Adapt archetypes for different cultural contexts
Antagonist builder: Specialized flow for villain archetypes
Voice samples: Audio clips showing archetype voice/tone

