âœ… 70%+ usage rate (users engage with archetype builder)
âœ… 85%+ completion rate (select an archetype)
âœ… 50%+ accept AI suggestions when offered
âœ… <3% error rate on archetype selection
âœ… Positive feedback in user testing (4+/5 satisfaction)
âœ… Clear differentiation between Quick and Comprehensive modes